Dialogs.Dialog: Let's have a lot of fun today.
I'm going to shift my eyes.
If we are together, you'll forget about the time.
A nice escort, let's get along okay?
I wake up early on a date. And you?
... I forgot what I was going to talk about when I saw your face.
Eh~? ...Huh? Didn't you call me? No...
I'd like to see your plans to go out.
I want to hurry, I want to relax... Dating is strange.
It's fun going out. Because it's with you.
If it's you, no matter what the weather is, it's a nice day for a date, right?
I will go with you anywhere▼
Don't look so much... Oh you. If you're staring, I won't lose.
I feel excited when it comes to dating. How about you?
Hey, what should we do on our next date. I'm kidding.
What if you stick together too much and you can't leave?
...Ah~, I'm sorry. I was able to see it▼
I want to use magic, so tomorrow don't comes. I'm kidding.
Forever~, I want to do this...
Aika's time is yours. Of course, your time is mine. I'm kidding.
Any place is a paradise? If we're together... I'm kidding.
I like it more and more only when I'm with you...
As it is, we are going somewhere far away... I'm kidding, it's a joke.
What should I do. I am very happy now.
...Don't look at me like that. If I can't sleep at night, it's your fault.
Girlfriend, lover, steady... Which one do you like best?
Is love the same thing? Something different?
What do you think of beign exclusive? ...I don't hate it, though.
What do you like about me? You know, come on▼
Is it okay to say "Lover's tie"? I like it▼
When you fall in love, it's really secret.
We are the happiest... What should I say?
Hey. If I call you, will come soon? Anywhere in the world▼
Hey, what are you thinking? I'm happy right now.
Isn't it so happy to be together?
Do you want to have me only for yourself?...I'm kidding.
I'm crazy about you. No, more.
I don't know what to do, so don't look too much...
...Did you like it? Because... I wanted to ask...
To school, to date. It's good, isn't it?
Do you want to review today's class? Fufu, a joke.
If we could meet like this every day... Fufu!
If I meet a friend, I might be a little shy...
I wish I had this much free time on my days off, would you?
Hey~. Let's go a little more slowly. Right?
I wish I had more time.
Let's be together more on our days off, right?
...Let's extend it for a little bit. I'm kidding.
I'm glad it was such a nice day♪
I hope it will be fine tomorrow.
Nice weather. The stars will look beautiful today, surely.
The clouds are thick, aren't they? I wonder if the sun will come out.
It's cloudy... I hope it doesn't rain.
I think it's easier to spend time in this cloudy weather.
When it's clear, you may see a rainbow. Looking forward to it?
Rainy days are a bit of fun.
If it's this hot, I'll sweat.
It's hot. I wonder if it will cool down soon.
Right now, it's a pleasant season.
The air of this season feels good.
The color of the sky is beautiful. Look, can see it?
The season of citrus and oranges. Right?
It's cold. Shall we go to a warmer place?
There are so many people today.
Don't look around because there are so many people!
There are a lot of people... I wonder if there is something.
It's not too crowded today. I'm glad.
I hope this doesn't get crowded, right?
I wonder if it's more crowded here.
There are no people, so you can relax.
Is it vacant? You might like this much.
Just the two of us? ...I feel a little better. I'm kidding.
You're up to something, aren't you?
Just the two of us... that's nice.
It's far. More, by the side... Right?
Hey, a little closer... it's okay.
I want you to feel a lot...
Hey, come on. We're wasting time.
You have plenty of time, right?
I have to make the most of my time.
I won't let you go yet.
You don't have enough time, do you?
I wish the day would be longer.
Hey, we can still be together, right?
When I'm with you, time goes by fast.
It's already time. I don't want to go home...
Hey, what are we going to do now?
Hey~, I wonder what we'll do.
Hmm, should we take it easy?
Emm, what should we do next?
I wonder what to do after this.
I there something you want to do, or want to go to?
Hey, what do we do after this... have you decided?
The next path is... I'll leave it to you♪
I hope there are good things today.
Fufu. I remembered what we were talking before.
Wait, there's something on you... yes▼
Yes, I'm in a good mood▼
Hey, why don't you skip it? A joke.
It's a date until you get home, right?
It was a very good date. I'm kidding.
Thank you. It was really fun♪
I wanna go again. Hey, we should do it soon.
Hey? Even if it's a dream, will you come to see me? I'm kidding.
When I'm with you, I'm really in trouble in no time.
It was a luxurious day. Next time, take care of me again▼
...Ah, I'm sorry. I will remember today.
Well, let's go there next time.
Look over there. Sounds good, doesn't it?
... I found something you were interested in. But it's secret.
It might be better over there. What do you think?
I wonder if there's something to do around here.
Ah~... It seems to have been just my imagination. I'm sorry.
There's still something you haven't seen, right?
What are you looking at? Fufu, would you like to go?
Hey, that... strange shape... what's that?
Do you know what's over there? I'm curious.
I feel light and I want to move my body.
Nice scenery... I guess it means that the air is clear.
Don't you feel relaxed near green scenery?
Are we moving? I'm fine whichever.
I wonder if I can find something unexpected.
Is there anything you're looking for?
If it's not that noisy, that's fine.
It's a problem if it's too cozy, isn't it?
In a little while, do you want to go somewhere else?
I think I'll make it the same as you♪
Ah, it's beautiful... it's boring. I'm kidding▼
The atmosphere in this room is reassuring...
I'm a little sleepy... I'm relieved that I'm here.
Shouldn't I look around here? Fufu!
Living alone or living together. Which one do you want? I'm kidding♪
I want to cook, clean, and do laundry...
Don't you feel lonely living alone? ...You say I'm lonely?
Just the two of us... Shall we try it?
...I don't want to go home. I'm kidding.
Here forever... Ah yes! It's nothing!
... Oh you. What do you say?
Emm... Yes. I'm a little nervous.
I clean it more carefully than usual▼
I feel that your room is brighter than usual.
There's nothing unusual. I'm not squeaking.
I won't go home today... I'm kidding.
I want to put you in my room...
Hey... do you like my room?
...Hey. You're not going home yet, are you?
Emm, drinks... not necessary? ...I see. Yes.
...I wonder why. I'm so excited right now...
Huh~? Ah~, I'm sorry. Emm~, what?
When you at me like that, I...
Yes, I will allow it. I'm kidding.
No good. Even if you put such a face, no.
Yes, that's right, isn't it? Fufu, together.
Is that so? I'm a little different, I guess.
I don't know what to say...
Thank you! I'm so happy, I don't know what to do...
No, that's all there is to it...
I don't know anymore. I'm kidding.
Are you going to say such a thing?
Fufu~, oh you. Don't be so pleased.
Do you look at girls other than me?
Don't worry? You're the only one I see...
Hmm, it's okay. I'm sorry for worrying you.
I see... Yes, that's right, isn't it?
I'm sorry. I don't really understand...
...A promise? You won't say such a thing anymore.
Geez, I won't talk to you anymore.
Emm~, I wonder if that's it?
Hmm... I don't think it's good.
